dct_title_s: Map of the Lower Wills Creek Basin showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Lower Wills Creek Basin
dct_description_sm: Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Lower Wills Creek Basin and quality of underground water.
Scale bar lower left corner of map.
"Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water"
Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
